  26,125,Mi est honest messenger vi
  26,126,Vi reverence DI obe me
  26,127,Mi ne pet vi por any wage my wage ven el Lord univers
  26,128,Vi cxarpent cxiu hill mansion vanity's sake
  26,129,Vi set buildings vi last forever
  26,130,Kaj when vi strik vi strik mercilessly
  26,131,Vi reverence DI obe me
