  26,146,Vi supoz vi las forever secure en this sxtat
  26,147,Vi gxu gxarden printemp
  26,148,crops daktil palm delicious frukt
  26,149,Vi carve mont luxurious mansions
  26,150,Vi reverence DI obe me
  26,151,Ne obe transgressors
