  26,153,Ili dir Vi sorcx
  26,154,Vi est ne plur than human us. Produkt mirakl se vi est truthful
  26,155,Li dir Here est kamel trink nur tag asign her; tag est different your specified tag de trink
  26,156,Do ne tusx her any harm lest vi incur retribution awesome tag
  26,157,Ili bucx her tiel incurred sorrow
