  26,165,Do vi hav seks vir all popol
  26,166,Vi forsake wives your Lord kre vi! Ja vi transgressing popol
  26,167,Ili dir vi refrain O Lot vi banished
  26,168,Li dir mi deplore your actions
  26,169,My Lord sav me my famili el their works
  26,170,Ni sav him all his famili
